OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,FThe government has announced new rules
OL,7,Fto protect people from being stuck in
OL,8,Fsubscriptions.
OL,10,FIt says the move will save a
OL,11,Fcollective #400 million a year.
OL,13,FITV News explains what the new rules
OL,14,Fare and how you could be affected.
OL,16,FWhat are the new rules?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
