FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775120518
OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,FCompanies offering subscriptions will
OL,7,Fhave to send reminders before free or
OL,8,Fdiscounted trials end or before
OL,9,Fcontracts of 12 months or more
OL,10,Fautomatically renew.
OL,12,FThey will also have to allow people to
OL,13,Feasily cancel a subscription online if
OL,14,Fthey originally signed up directly
OL,15,Fthrough the company, which should
OL,16,Fprevent lengthy waits on the phone to
OL,17,Fend a contract.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775120518
OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,FThere will be a 14-day cooling off
OL,7,Fperiod after a free or discounted
OL,8,Ftrial ends, or when a contract renews
OL,9,Ffor 12 months or longer.
OL,11,FWhich organisations are exempt?
OL,13,FThe new rules won't apply to certain
OL,14,Fmembership of charitable, cultural and
OL,15,Fheritage organisations because of
OL,16,F"their role in preserving and
OL,17,Fproviding access to locations and
OL,18,Fcultural collections".
OL,20,FWhen will the new rules apply?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
