OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,FThe new rules should come into place
OL,7,Fsometime next year.
OL,9,FHow many people will be affected?
OL,11,FThere are 155 million active
OL,12,Fsubscriptions held by people across
OL,13,Fthe UK, with almost 10 million of them
OL,14,Fbelieved to be unwanted, the
OL,15,Fgovernment said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
