FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775120518
OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,FMore than 3.5 million people are being
OL,7,F"quietly rolled" from free or
OL,8,Fdiscounted trials into fully costed
OL,9,Fcontracts, while another 1.3 million
OL,10,Fare caught out by unexpected
OL,11,Fautorenewals, it added.
OL,13,FHow much money will be saved?
OL,15,FThe government said the new rules
OL,16,Fcould save people around #14 a month
OL,17,Fon average per unwanted subscription,
OL,18,For almost #170 a year.
OL,20,FCollectively, that adds up to #400
OL,21,Fmillion a year.
