OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,FWhy are these rules being introduced?
OL,8,FMinister for Consumer Protection Kate
OL,9,FDearden said there's "nothing more
OL,10,Ffrustrating than seeing money you've
OL,11,Fworked hard for, disappear from your
OL,12,Faccount for a subscription you've
OL,13,Fforgotten you had".
OL,15,F"These new rules will put consumers
OL,16,Fback in control of their money `
OL,17,Fmaking subscriptions clearer, fairer
OL,18,Fand far easier to cancel," she added.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
