OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSo-called "subscription traps" can be
OL,12,F"costly and wreak havoc" on finances,
OL,13,FWhich? head of consumer rights policy
OL,14,FSue Davies said.
OL,16,F"The strengthening of subscription
OL,17,Flaws will be welcome news for those
OL,18,Fstruggling with rising costs.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
