OL,3,CWhat are the new rules on automatic
OL,4,Csubscription renewals?
OL,6,F"These new rules will help put
OL,7,Fconsumers in the driving seat with
OL,8,Fproper transparency and protection."
OL,10,FHow can you avoid subscription traps
OL,11,Fin the meantime?
OL,13,FGet Safe Online says subscription
OL,14,Ftraps are particularly common with
OL,15,Fproducts such as slimming pills,
OL,16,Fhealth foods, pharmaceuticals and anti-
OL,17,Faging products, but any company can
OL,18,Fuse them.
OL,20,FThe online safety organisation
OL,21,Frecommends:
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]
